WEBVTT

00:54.013 --> 00:54.747
(This drama is a work of fiction.)

00:54.747 --> 00:55.548
(All characters, organizations,
and events in this drama are fictitious.)

00:55.548 --> 00:56.282
(This drama complied
with production guidelines...)

00:56.282 --> 00:57.016
(for filming child actors and animals.)

01:01.521 --> 01:02.755
What are you going to do now?

01:04.023 --> 01:07.059
The fact that Myo Jin
found out about the three of us...

01:07.059 --> 01:08.161
was not, like you thought,

01:08.995 --> 01:11.998
something that just
came back to her naturally over time.

01:13.833 --> 01:14.967
That doesn't make sense.

01:16.335 --> 01:17.837
She went around looking everywhere,

01:19.205 --> 01:21.674
meeting people, and learned it that way.

01:24.277 --> 01:26.879
I didn't think
she'd find out this quickly.

01:27.947 --> 01:28.848
What matters is...

01:29.949 --> 01:32.251
she's not going to sit still
from here on out.

01:36.055 --> 01:36.889
Then,

01:37.890 --> 01:39.225
what am I supposed to do?

01:40.193 --> 01:41.093
Stop her.

01:41.994 --> 01:42.829
Do you think...

01:43.896 --> 01:44.831
that'll be possible?

01:47.366 --> 01:49.836
Do you think you can afford
to be thinking like that right now?

01:50.670 --> 01:51.838
If this goes any further,

01:52.238 --> 01:54.240
have you imagined what will happen to us?

01:56.075 --> 01:57.510
You can't let it go any further.

01:58.878 --> 02:00.146
You have no choice.

02:00.546 --> 02:01.814
Protecting Myo Jin...

02:03.082 --> 02:04.183
means protecting everyone.

02:07.587 --> 02:08.855
You look like you're hesitating.

02:10.323 --> 02:11.224
Why?

02:11.824 --> 02:12.792
You're not confident?

02:14.527 --> 02:18.030
Then should we just give up on everything?

02:18.030 --> 02:18.931
Shut up!

02:50.897 --> 02:52.565
You don't care that the chairman died,

02:52.999 --> 02:55.101
and you just want to grab
what you can and run?

02:55.101 --> 02:56.002
Is that it?

02:56.002 --> 02:57.804
Do you think I don't know
what you're really after?

02:58.437 --> 02:59.872
I will expose
the one who did that to the chairman...

03:00.439 --> 03:01.707
soon enough.

03:01.707 --> 03:04.477
If the police can't,
I'll expose him myself.

03:04.677 --> 03:06.212
I think I know who it is.

03:06.679 --> 03:07.980
You bastard.

03:21.994 --> 03:25.364
(Caught)

03:26.432 --> 03:27.300
Yeah.

03:27.667 --> 03:28.634
Yeah, I know.

03:29.235 --> 03:31.170
We just need to watch a little longer.

03:31.838 --> 03:34.507
Yeah, I'd appreciate that.

03:40.112 --> 03:41.347
It's a relief.

03:41.347 --> 03:42.582
He's in the ICU right now,

03:42.582 --> 03:43.950
but they say he'll live.

03:47.153 --> 03:49.455
But are you okay?

03:52.124 --> 03:54.427
He beat me even after I said I was a cop.

03:56.028 --> 03:57.530
Just let him wake up.

03:58.197 --> 03:59.866
I'll put him right back in the hospital.

04:02.535 --> 04:05.471
Anyway, business is business. Let's see.

04:05.705 --> 04:06.706
The copy worked fine, right?

04:08.741 --> 04:10.143
- Here.
- Okay.

04:10.143 --> 04:13.279
I planned it all out in advance,

04:13.913 --> 04:15.815
so that should've been plenty of time.

04:16.349 --> 04:17.950
Let's check it first.

04:18.718 --> 04:21.053
All you need to check
in someone's phone...

04:21.621 --> 04:22.722
is the texts.

04:23.523 --> 04:24.624
Her name was Hee Su, right?

04:24.924 --> 04:26.359
Yes. Choi Hee Su.

04:26.359 --> 04:28.694
Once we check
what messages they exchanged,

04:28.694 --> 04:30.196
the answer will be clear.

04:30.429 --> 04:33.800
The answer to
what she was trying so hard to hide,

04:34.133 --> 04:36.068
and how you are connected to all this.

04:36.969 --> 04:38.704
Choi Hee Su.

04:39.005 --> 04:39.939
Choi Hee Su.

04:41.040 --> 04:42.475
Choi Hee Su.

04:42.475 --> 04:43.276
There!

04:43.643 --> 04:44.811
Here's Choi Hee Su.

04:45.912 --> 04:47.713
Yes.

04:48.414 --> 04:50.650
So she really was being blackmailed.

04:51.484 --> 04:52.852
But all this says...

04:53.586 --> 04:55.388
is to do exactly what he says.

04:55.888 --> 04:57.824
Usually, people ask for money.

04:57.824 --> 04:58.825
There.

04:59.425 --> 05:01.460
From here on,
Lee Jong Su's name keeps coming up.

05:01.928 --> 05:03.029
Let's see.

05:03.029 --> 05:04.163
Yes!

05:04.864 --> 05:06.466
I knew it.

05:06.999 --> 05:07.834
What? 300,000 dollars?

05:08.701 --> 05:09.669
At once?

05:10.837 --> 05:11.737
What?

05:11.737 --> 05:13.573
Whatever he had on her, it was serious.

05:13.573 --> 05:14.507
It had to be.

05:14.774 --> 05:16.275
- Scroll down more.
- Okay.

05:17.143 --> 05:20.179
Even after getting the money,
he kept threatening her.

05:20.179 --> 05:21.714
What's this?

05:22.548 --> 05:25.618
But here, he's sending pictures of a man.

05:26.252 --> 05:27.453
Was this blackmail too?

05:30.056 --> 05:30.890
This...

05:31.858 --> 05:33.092
This is...

05:33.092 --> 05:33.960
But...

05:34.327 --> 05:36.028
Why...

05:40.433 --> 05:41.267
This...

05:42.635 --> 05:43.836
This...

05:43.836 --> 05:45.238
So that's what it was?

05:57.850 --> 05:59.385
They'll care a lot about this.

05:59.652 --> 06:02.188
I put a little pressure on them...

06:02.188 --> 06:03.556
because it's my only daughter's gallery.

06:04.590 --> 06:07.193
You're a five-term lawmaker
up for re-election.

06:07.760 --> 06:08.995
So I'm sure they'll do a good job.

06:10.429 --> 06:13.499
But among the merchants
who hover around politicians,

06:14.167 --> 06:15.668
there aren't many decent ones.

06:16.335 --> 06:18.571
"Merchants?"

06:18.571 --> 06:21.407
He's top-level in Korean architecture.

06:22.708 --> 06:24.744
I don't know how close you are,

06:25.745 --> 06:27.280
but is it okay to ask a favor like this?

06:28.447 --> 06:30.316
The construction costs must be enormous.

06:31.184 --> 06:33.319
I'll handle it.

06:35.421 --> 06:36.222
What a surprise.

06:36.856 --> 06:39.192
What brings you here
all of a sudden, Mr. Cho?

06:40.226 --> 06:42.195
Something urgent came up
that I needed to discuss,

06:42.195 --> 06:43.996
and I heard you were here, sir.

06:44.263 --> 06:45.131
I see.

06:45.431 --> 06:46.299
Take a seat.

06:52.605 --> 06:54.407
What is it you wanted to discuss?

06:54.407 --> 06:55.541
It's just that,

06:56.175 --> 06:58.544
as you said, CEO Oh Sang Il seems...

06:58.544 --> 07:00.513
to have actually met with Ryu Jun Ho.

07:00.980 --> 07:04.350
So that Ryu Jun Ho really did
crawl in through a back door.

07:04.884 --> 07:08.254
It's something I could laugh off myself,

07:08.554 --> 07:11.290
but if word of this somehow gets out,

07:12.225 --> 07:14.227
the image of the competition hosts...

07:18.397 --> 07:19.432
But...

07:20.032 --> 07:22.235
isn't your information a little late?

07:22.702 --> 07:23.636
Pardon?

07:23.636 --> 07:25.438
Yesterday,

07:25.438 --> 07:27.507
the organizers
apparently held discussions...

07:27.507 --> 07:31.277
about new internal rules
related to this competition.

07:32.845 --> 07:35.448
It seems to have happened
at CEO Oh's strong request.

07:37.083 --> 07:40.753
Wouldn't it be more urgent
to find out what that is?

07:47.693 --> 07:49.028
People...

07:49.028 --> 07:50.396
make mistakes sometimes,

07:50.930 --> 07:52.799
and get shaken down too.

07:53.299 --> 07:55.568
That's what happens
when you get caught in a love triangle.

07:55.568 --> 07:57.837
Well, spilled water is spilled water.

07:57.837 --> 08:00.339
You wipe it clean
and make sure it doesn't happen again.

08:04.477 --> 08:06.212
There's this saying.

08:06.813 --> 08:09.081
Even if you get hit by the first arrow,
don't get hit by the second.

08:09.282 --> 08:12.285
Don't beat yourself up
over something that's already...

08:12.285 --> 08:13.519
- Lee Jong Su.
- You startled me.

08:13.519 --> 08:14.854
Why was he tormenting Hee Su?

08:15.188 --> 08:17.190
Isn't it obvious? For money.

08:17.190 --> 08:19.392
You saw it.
He extorted 300,000 in one shot.

08:19.826 --> 08:20.693
No.

08:21.294 --> 08:22.261
It wasn't about money.

08:22.461 --> 08:23.396
It wasn't?

08:23.396 --> 08:24.764
Hee Su was the victim.

08:25.498 --> 08:26.632
With those photos,

08:26.632 --> 08:28.367
the people he should've
been threatening...

08:28.367 --> 08:30.736
weren't Hee Su, but Ryu Jun Ho and me.

08:31.003 --> 08:32.605
If money was the goal,
that's what makes sense.

08:33.506 --> 08:34.373
Is that so?

08:35.708 --> 08:37.510
Lee Jong Su had another reason.

08:38.244 --> 08:39.745
And Hee Su was afraid of that.

08:41.247 --> 08:42.748
Something that hurt Hee Su...

08:44.350 --> 08:46.219
more than my relationship with Ryu Jun Ho.

09:08.875 --> 09:09.709
Here.

09:12.912 --> 09:14.380
Hamburgers.

09:15.081 --> 09:17.116
It's late, so go inside.

09:18.017 --> 09:19.352
Leave one for your brother.

09:24.490 --> 09:25.358
Sir.

09:26.225 --> 09:27.093
Yeah?

09:27.460 --> 09:29.262
Are you rich?

09:30.029 --> 09:30.863
Rich?

09:30.863 --> 09:31.731
Yes.

09:33.399 --> 09:34.233
Sure.

09:34.667 --> 09:35.535
I'm rich.

09:36.235 --> 09:37.637
How rich?

09:38.604 --> 09:39.972
Rich enough...

09:40.873 --> 09:42.441
to buy you that bread every single day.

09:43.075 --> 09:43.910
Cool.

09:45.745 --> 09:48.681
But where did all your money come from?

09:50.416 --> 09:51.551
How...

09:51.551 --> 09:53.719
do I get rich like you?

10:20.580 --> 10:21.547
Who are you people?

10:24.217 --> 10:24.984
Answer me.

10:57.817 --> 10:58.684
Hey.

11:00.753 --> 11:02.221
Stop this.

11:02.588 --> 11:04.157
This is too much.

11:04.157 --> 11:06.459
Why are you doing this
like a bunch of idiots?

11:07.360 --> 11:08.928
Have some common sense.

11:09.896 --> 11:11.464
At this point,

11:11.464 --> 11:12.932
he should have figured it out...

11:14.734 --> 11:16.235
since he's smart and quick on the uptake.

11:17.270 --> 11:18.404
Mr. Ryu.

11:23.442 --> 11:24.644
Isn't that right?

11:25.678 --> 11:28.447
CEO Ryu Jun Ho of Mono Architecture.

11:35.721 --> 11:37.223
Did your heart skip a beat?

11:38.491 --> 11:40.326
Did you think if you pulled strings
behind the scenes,

11:40.893 --> 11:42.295
no one would know?

11:43.095 --> 11:45.364
When the stench is this thick everywhere?

11:47.567 --> 11:49.569
Stay out of this competition.

11:50.803 --> 11:52.238
Today's just a warning.

11:52.872 --> 11:55.274
If I hear your name again,

11:55.942 --> 11:56.843
then,

11:58.744 --> 12:00.913
even that handsome face I spared today...

12:03.883 --> 12:05.451
won't survive.

12:10.022 --> 12:11.123
Let's go.

12:21.200 --> 12:23.669
Hey, long time no see.

12:23.669 --> 12:24.504
Yes.

12:25.304 --> 12:26.639
You eat well.

12:26.639 --> 12:28.574
Two servings are gone just like that.

12:30.877 --> 12:33.980
But is it really that important
to know where Detective Kang is?

12:33.980 --> 12:35.348
No way.

12:35.348 --> 12:36.883
I can easily find out.

12:37.750 --> 12:38.951
Then why...

12:38.951 --> 12:41.187
I'm just grateful, that's all.

12:42.488 --> 12:43.523
Because from here on,

12:44.090 --> 12:45.558
there's something I need you to tell me.

12:46.759 --> 12:47.627
Sorry?

12:47.894 --> 12:49.195
Something happened
to Detective Kang, right?

12:49.495 --> 12:51.664
He didn't just step away
from the villa case, right?

12:56.402 --> 12:57.403
How would I know?

12:58.037 --> 12:58.838
Hey.

12:59.505 --> 13:00.706
When you got here,

13:00.706 --> 13:02.408
it was Detective Kang
who taught you everything, right?

13:02.875 --> 13:03.776
I...

13:04.944 --> 13:07.113
practically raised Detective Kang
from diapers.

13:11.851 --> 13:13.619
Before Detective Kang quit,

13:14.253 --> 13:16.022
you two drank together
every night for a month.

13:16.689 --> 13:17.857
What did the two of you talk about?

13:18.558 --> 13:21.460
If I say the wrong thing
and something blows up...

13:22.328 --> 13:23.696
Hey, look at me.

13:25.965 --> 13:27.366
I need your help.

13:27.900 --> 13:30.069
We have to bring
Detective Kang back, don't we?

13:38.010 --> 13:40.980
Detective Kang didn't just quit.

13:41.747 --> 13:44.784
Every time we drank,
he kept saying he couldn't trust anyone.

13:46.185 --> 13:47.987
He said he found out something important,

13:47.987 --> 13:50.289
but that he couldn't step in right now.

13:50.289 --> 13:51.157
What was it?

13:51.157 --> 13:52.225
I really don't know that.

13:55.094 --> 13:57.096
He just said...

13:57.096 --> 13:59.499
he'd rather take it to the grave
than let it out halfway.

14:21.320 --> 14:22.188
That's empty.

14:51.317 --> 14:52.418
Were you watching me?

14:53.052 --> 14:54.453
You looked troubled.

14:56.022 --> 14:57.723
I had some thinking to do too.

15:01.894 --> 15:04.230
On sports day back in elementary school,

15:04.230 --> 15:06.599
there was this event
called Find-a-Person Race.

15:07.934 --> 15:09.635
I loved it...

15:11.270 --> 15:13.072
because I was confident about running.

15:15.441 --> 15:17.643
When it was my turn,

15:17.643 --> 15:19.946
I picked a slip of paper,

15:19.946 --> 15:20.847
and on it...

15:22.515 --> 15:24.050
was written, "Mom."

15:26.786 --> 15:29.188
The person who wrote that
would never have known...

15:30.056 --> 15:30.923
that...

15:32.291 --> 15:36.462
a kid without a mother
would be the one to pick it.

15:39.765 --> 15:40.666
Back then,

15:41.267 --> 15:43.769
I think I realized something.

15:45.638 --> 15:46.806
Rules...

15:48.774 --> 15:50.743
aren't made...

15:52.378 --> 15:55.081
for the people without,
but for the people with.

16:01.087 --> 16:04.123
I think it was around then...

16:05.691 --> 16:08.861
that I learned my mom and dad
had died in an accident,

16:10.496 --> 16:11.931
not gone to America to make money.

16:15.568 --> 16:18.571
I begged my grandmother for days...

16:20.106 --> 16:21.073
to tell me the truth.

16:21.607 --> 16:23.843
So what did you do?

16:26.179 --> 16:28.681
I just grabbed the hand
of a woman who looked like a mom and ran.

16:30.483 --> 16:31.684
With the whole school watching,

16:32.919 --> 16:35.855
I didn't want anyone to know
I didn't have a mother.

16:45.498 --> 16:48.434
A man named Mr. Cho
came to see my father today,

16:49.902 --> 16:51.370
and I heard him talking about you.

16:56.209 --> 16:57.210
It was him, wasn't it?

17:00.246 --> 17:01.514
Thanks to that, it all clicked.

17:03.282 --> 17:06.252
I now know what was happening...

17:08.154 --> 17:09.121
without me knowing.

17:21.901 --> 17:22.768
I'm curious...

17:23.169 --> 17:24.170
about that race that day.

17:31.944 --> 17:33.880
I ran like crazy and came in first.

17:35.915 --> 17:37.183
I didn't want to lose...

17:38.251 --> 17:39.418
in that situation.

17:40.353 --> 17:42.989
Coming in first that day
must've felt even better than usual.

17:43.890 --> 17:44.924
But somehow,

17:46.225 --> 17:48.127
I don't think it did.

18:07.880 --> 18:10.449
(L Karaoke Bar)

18:11.350 --> 18:12.351
Damn it.

18:14.554 --> 18:16.322
Why isn't this bastard answering?

18:16.322 --> 18:18.024
He usually picks up right away.

18:18.524 --> 18:19.892
Are you sure he runs a bar?

18:20.693 --> 18:21.494
Yes.

18:23.262 --> 18:24.530
Then what's with this?

18:24.530 --> 18:25.598
How would I know?

18:25.598 --> 18:27.166
All I have to do is hand him over
and take the money.

18:31.571 --> 18:32.939
I'll try him again right now.

18:34.307 --> 18:35.608
Leave it.

18:35.608 --> 18:36.776
He'll call.

18:37.310 --> 18:38.644
Don't do anything stupid.

18:38.644 --> 18:40.746
You just stay with us.

18:40.746 --> 18:42.315
What brings you here?

18:48.387 --> 18:49.255
Sir.

18:49.589 --> 18:51.591
Do you run a place in this building?

18:51.924 --> 18:54.827
I run the lottery shop right up front.

18:54.827 --> 18:55.728
I see.

18:56.562 --> 18:58.264
Is this bar doing business?

18:59.232 --> 19:01.734
I've got a gathering
with old hometown friends tomorrow,

19:01.734 --> 19:03.069
but the place is closed.

19:03.336 --> 19:04.704
There'll be about 30 of us.

19:06.706 --> 19:09.609
This place barely opens.

19:09.976 --> 19:11.611
That owner...

19:12.245 --> 19:14.847
only comes
when he feels like doing business.

19:16.415 --> 19:19.685
But are there really 30 people coming?

19:21.220 --> 19:22.455
It's a couples' gathering.

19:23.723 --> 19:24.891
Too bad.

19:24.891 --> 19:25.858
Let's go somewhere else.

19:25.858 --> 19:27.760
Hang on.

19:28.294 --> 19:29.562
I know his number.

19:32.431 --> 19:34.500
A guy who claims he runs a business...

19:34.500 --> 19:36.102
That little punk.

19:36.102 --> 19:38.704
The person you are calling is unavailable.
Please leave a message after the beep.

19:38.704 --> 19:39.806
Unbelievable.

19:40.373 --> 19:42.575
Why even carry a phone around?

19:44.510 --> 19:45.378
But...

19:45.978 --> 19:47.413
the way you talk.

19:48.714 --> 19:50.149
Are you Korean Chinese?

19:51.150 --> 19:52.952
Your Korean's good.

19:54.821 --> 19:56.689
Korean Chinese? No.

19:58.324 --> 19:59.425
That bastard.

20:02.061 --> 20:03.963
Anyway, thank you.

20:07.066 --> 20:10.036
He lost all those customers.

20:10.536 --> 20:12.004
He's my son, but still,

20:12.305 --> 20:15.608
he's so pathetic.

20:17.210 --> 20:19.312
I'm so dumbfounded I can't even speak.

20:20.379 --> 20:22.415
You pig who waddles around
and can't even run...

20:22.415 --> 20:23.683
tried to escape?

20:23.683 --> 20:24.784
Sir, I'm sorry.

20:24.784 --> 20:26.819
You two were having
an important conversation.

20:28.521 --> 20:31.023
I'll lose weight right away
and never run again.

20:31.757 --> 20:32.992
Yes, I'll take the beating.

20:35.628 --> 20:38.297
Just hit me somewhere else, please.

20:38.297 --> 20:39.632
I really hate it in here.

20:40.032 --> 20:41.100
You can hit me twice as much.

20:41.100 --> 20:42.902
Please, okay?

20:42.902 --> 20:43.769
Sir.

20:43.769 --> 20:44.837
Shut your mouth.

20:55.648 --> 20:56.682
What's that one?

20:57.917 --> 20:59.185
Women come here too?

20:59.185 --> 21:01.287
That's not a woman. That's a man.

21:07.393 --> 21:08.261
You.

21:09.829 --> 21:10.797
Turn around.

21:17.203 --> 21:18.204
How'd you end up here?

21:19.472 --> 21:20.439
That punk there...

21:20.439 --> 21:22.842
got dragged in for trying to rape
Mr. Chang at the butcher shop out front.

21:23.209 --> 21:24.510
They say he's as strong as an ox.

21:24.510 --> 21:26.179
Once he grabs hold, he goes all night.

21:26.946 --> 21:28.681
I'm too unnerved to reflect properly.

21:28.681 --> 21:30.716
Can he reflect somewhere else instead?

21:32.385 --> 21:33.486
He's scaring me.

21:34.854 --> 21:35.788
Everybody out.

21:37.056 --> 21:38.157
Can't you hear me?

21:41.160 --> 21:43.429
Your reflection time is over.

21:43.429 --> 21:45.031
Go back to making a living.

21:46.966 --> 21:48.668
Thank you.

21:48.668 --> 21:49.735
Thank you.

21:49.735 --> 21:50.570
You.

21:54.307 --> 21:55.107
You.

21:57.176 --> 21:58.211
You stay.

21:58.478 --> 21:59.612
I've got a job for you.

22:01.581 --> 22:03.282
What do you need me to do?

22:03.282 --> 22:05.551
Teach that little bastard a lesson.

22:06.853 --> 22:08.921
As for how, use whatever you're best at.

22:13.359 --> 22:14.393
I don't want to.

22:14.794 --> 22:16.496
What if someone comes in all of a sudden?

22:16.963 --> 22:17.997
It's embarrassing.

22:17.997 --> 22:19.765
I'll lock it from the outside.

22:19.765 --> 22:20.933
Don't worry.

22:22.802 --> 22:25.538
How much time do I get?

22:25.905 --> 22:27.874
You can go all night, can't you?

22:27.874 --> 22:28.708
What?

22:29.842 --> 22:30.710
Thank you.

22:31.878 --> 22:32.845
Thank you.

22:32.845 --> 22:34.380
Sir, what are you saying?

22:34.680 --> 22:35.948
What do you mean?

22:35.948 --> 22:37.216
I'll make this punk...

22:37.216 --> 22:39.418
a brand-new man.

22:42.555 --> 22:46.058
(Reflection)

23:00.940 --> 23:02.608
Wang Gi Cheol, that bastard.

23:14.987 --> 23:16.823
(Wang Gi Cheol)

23:16.823 --> 23:17.757
(Don't let your guard down.)

23:17.757 --> 23:18.791
(They're way smarter
than either you or me.)

23:18.791 --> 23:19.959
(And don't you give up either.)

23:24.630 --> 23:27.099
The fiancé of Mono Group's
only daughter...

23:27.099 --> 23:29.535
cheated with her friend
and pissed her off.

23:30.269 --> 23:31.337
How humiliating is that?

23:32.572 --> 23:36.075
But just for that, hundreds of thousands?

23:36.876 --> 23:38.244
That's too weak.

23:39.445 --> 23:43.149
Like Ham Myo Jin said,
there has to be a stronger reason.

23:43.883 --> 23:46.552
(Ham Myo Jin)

23:48.354 --> 23:49.255
Ms. Ham.

23:49.655 --> 23:50.690
We were wrong.

23:51.324 --> 23:53.493
- We've been thinking all wrong.
- About what?

23:53.659 --> 23:56.095
From the start, Lee Jong Su
didn't care about Hee Su at all.

23:56.896 --> 23:59.098
He tormented Hee Su
to get to Chairman Choi Young Ho.

23:59.098 --> 24:01.167
Lee Jong Su was after
Chairman Choi Young Ho? Why?

24:01.167 --> 24:04.504
There are texts between Lee Jong Su
and someone named Wang Gi Cheol.

24:04.504 --> 24:05.805
They were talking about money,

24:05.805 --> 24:07.707
and saying they needed
to meet Chairman Choi Young Ho.

24:07.707 --> 24:08.975
That's it.

24:09.242 --> 24:10.309
If someone's threatening...

24:10.309 --> 24:11.811
to expose the private life
of his only daughter,

24:11.811 --> 24:13.179
what parent would just let that happen?

24:13.179 --> 24:14.447
And the price becomes whatever they ask.

24:14.447 --> 24:15.882
But that's not all.

24:16.716 --> 24:18.184
There's something else strange here.

24:18.618 --> 24:22.155
Lee Jong Su keeps bringing up my name
to someone named Wang Gi Cheol...

24:22.155 --> 24:23.489
like he knows me.

24:23.756 --> 24:25.691
Do you happen to know
someone named Wang Gi Cheol?

24:25.691 --> 24:26.826
Wang Gi Cheol?

24:26.826 --> 24:27.727
No.

24:28.161 --> 24:29.162
I don't.

24:29.162 --> 24:30.229
What does he say?

24:30.530 --> 24:32.465
He keeps talking
about Chairman Choi Young Ho and me,

24:32.799 --> 24:33.833
and it's all about money.

24:36.536 --> 24:38.604
What connection do I even have
to Chairman Choi Young Ho?

24:38.604 --> 24:40.506
This is driving me crazy.

24:40.506 --> 24:41.374
This won't do.

24:41.374 --> 24:43.776
Tomorrow,
even if I have to kill Lee Jong Su,

24:43.776 --> 24:45.211
- I'm getting the truth out of him.
- Wait a second.

24:46.679 --> 24:47.747
I'll call you back.

24:56.222 --> 24:57.557
(Choi Young Ho's daughter
seems to be returning soon.)

24:57.557 --> 24:58.825
(Jeongun Trading at 6 p.m.)

24:58.825 --> 25:00.059
(Chairman Choi Young Ho
is backing Ryu Jun Ho's business.)

25:00.059 --> 25:01.427
(Tracking Chairman Choi's whereabouts
through Choi Hee Su and Ryu Jun Ho)

25:04.964 --> 25:05.932
You vicious bitch.

25:06.365 --> 25:07.266
Wasn't it enough...

25:08.267 --> 25:09.469
that two people died?

25:11.804 --> 25:12.939
You could've stopped there...

25:14.040 --> 25:15.041
with your revenge.

25:30.590 --> 25:32.792
The list of judges for the competition
has been announced.

25:33.626 --> 25:36.295
CEO Oh Sang Il is listed
as the head judge.

25:37.563 --> 25:38.798
The eligibility criteria...

25:38.798 --> 25:40.800
for entering the competition
have also been changed.

25:41.767 --> 25:43.503
Industry experience
and awards have been removed,

25:44.137 --> 25:46.305
and they say the focus will be...

25:46.305 --> 25:48.608
solely on evaluating current ability
as it relates to this competition.

25:52.445 --> 25:54.480
What modern architects need...

25:54.480 --> 25:58.017
for the essence
of the works they create...

25:58.017 --> 25:59.886
is silence.

25:59.886 --> 26:01.420
When do you think...

26:02.455 --> 26:04.557
architects step out of the silence...

26:04.557 --> 26:06.659
you just spoke of, Mr. Ryu?

26:06.659 --> 26:08.794
I believe silence must continue.

26:08.794 --> 26:09.629
But...

26:10.563 --> 26:14.634
only through communion and communication
between the building and people...

26:14.634 --> 26:15.535
can one...

26:15.535 --> 26:17.670
finally step out of that silence.

26:21.741 --> 26:24.477
There's something
people are mistaken about.

26:25.545 --> 26:26.712
Because they focus...

26:28.014 --> 26:30.049
only on a building's exterior
and function,

26:30.049 --> 26:32.185
they fail to see
that the philosophy and soul...

26:32.185 --> 26:33.920
that should be inside it are disappearing.

26:34.921 --> 26:37.190
Could you tell me
what direction you're headed in,

26:38.591 --> 26:39.625
Mr. Ryu?

26:41.227 --> 26:43.329
"There is no such thing as architecture,"

26:44.697 --> 26:45.965
"only architects."

26:47.033 --> 26:48.134
There's a saying like that.

26:48.701 --> 26:50.703
It's also a creed I remind myself of...

26:52.004 --> 26:53.306
whenever I work.

26:56.075 --> 26:59.045
It seems CEO Oh Sang Il
personally requested...

26:59.378 --> 27:01.314
the Ministry of Culture to change
the competition eligibility rules.

27:03.916 --> 27:04.917
That's good news.

27:07.653 --> 27:08.621
Two hundred thousand?

27:08.621 --> 27:09.455
In cash?

27:10.022 --> 27:10.857
Right away?

27:11.257 --> 27:12.992
Hey, people can hear you.

27:13.726 --> 27:15.094
Do you want me to get you a mic?

27:15.795 --> 27:17.964
But if I bring this to you
and you start talking nonsense...

27:17.964 --> 27:19.198
Come on.

27:19.432 --> 27:21.501
I'm telling you,
they're like right and left hands.

27:22.869 --> 27:24.170
Two hundred thousand?

27:25.071 --> 27:26.272
You said she's pretty, right?

27:27.106 --> 27:28.040
And slim too?

27:28.040 --> 27:29.809
That much I can guarantee.

27:30.877 --> 27:31.944
"Who am I? Where am I?"

27:31.944 --> 27:34.413
She's like that every single day,
all mixed up.

27:34.413 --> 27:35.448
What are you saying?

27:35.781 --> 27:38.618
I'm saying she's philosophical.

27:38.885 --> 27:40.620
She's tall and sexy.

27:43.856 --> 27:44.657
Okay.

27:47.627 --> 27:49.128
Why is he sleeping like that?

27:49.328 --> 27:50.563
Is that really reflecting?

27:50.563 --> 27:52.198
He had some things happen to him.

27:52.198 --> 27:53.666
He must've had a rough time.

27:56.702 --> 27:58.204
It looks like he lost some weight.

27:59.272 --> 28:00.373
Did you not feed him anything?

28:00.540 --> 28:02.675
He didn't eat or sleep all night.

28:02.675 --> 28:03.743
He just got educated.

28:05.611 --> 28:07.113
What are you going to do?

28:07.713 --> 28:09.849
Don't you know how I work?

28:10.316 --> 28:11.150
All right.

28:18.191 --> 28:19.025
Excuse me.

28:20.193 --> 28:20.960
Excuse me.

28:21.994 --> 28:25.031
I'm sorry to interrupt you two,

28:26.032 --> 28:27.500
but I have something to say.

28:28.100 --> 28:29.735
At this point, I'd rather die...

28:31.737 --> 28:33.406
than keep living like this.

28:34.073 --> 28:36.342
What, are you asking me to kill you?

28:38.711 --> 28:39.679
No, that's not it.

28:40.079 --> 28:43.015
Actually, I have a lot of money.

28:44.116 --> 28:45.184
Let's settle this.

28:45.585 --> 28:46.486
I mean, at this point,

28:48.087 --> 28:49.622
I've suffered enough, haven't I?

28:51.190 --> 28:52.625
You want to pay me?

28:52.859 --> 28:53.659
Are you rich?

28:57.296 --> 28:58.698
I'll give you as much as you want.

28:58.698 --> 28:59.932
Not a penny less.

28:59.932 --> 29:02.735
Now that we're talking about it,
I'll transfer it right now.

29:02.735 --> 29:03.970
Nice and clean, okay?

29:07.607 --> 29:08.407
You.

29:09.842 --> 29:11.978
Those people you scammed and beat up.

29:11.978 --> 29:12.879
Do you know who they were?

29:14.147 --> 29:16.782
They're his only little brother
and his coworkers.

29:17.083 --> 29:19.118
Money alone won't solve this, you idiot.

29:19.519 --> 29:20.753
Fuck.

29:25.158 --> 29:27.059
(L Karaoke Bar An Woo Sik)

29:32.632 --> 29:33.599
He really came.

29:35.368 --> 29:36.402
Did you set it up right?

29:36.736 --> 29:38.704
His location will show up
directly on my end.

29:38.704 --> 29:40.907
But the call has to last
at least a minute.

29:41.307 --> 29:43.276
If you try anything funny,
you'll die on the spot.

29:43.276 --> 29:44.277
No way.

29:44.277 --> 29:45.311
Absolutely not.

29:45.678 --> 29:46.512
One minute.

29:46.512 --> 29:47.413
One minute.

29:52.351 --> 29:53.219
Okay.

29:57.290 --> 29:58.257
Hello?

29:59.058 --> 30:01.494
Are you the guy who's so hard to reach?

30:01.494 --> 30:02.728
What are you, my girlfriend?

30:03.329 --> 30:04.997
Why do you keep calling?

30:04.997 --> 30:07.233
Business must be good.

30:07.233 --> 30:08.568
So what, I'm not worth money anymore?

30:08.568 --> 30:10.970
No way.

30:10.970 --> 30:12.004
But what's this?

30:12.004 --> 30:13.940
You sound like something good happened.

30:13.940 --> 30:16.075
A group booking came in,
and the headcount's pretty big.

30:16.476 --> 30:17.410
How many?

30:17.810 --> 30:18.711
Well,

30:20.480 --> 30:21.581
three.

30:21.781 --> 30:22.782
What? Three?

30:24.717 --> 30:27.787
That was a joke. Thirty.

30:27.787 --> 30:28.955
That's huge.

30:28.955 --> 30:30.957
That's too many for you, right?

30:30.957 --> 30:33.626
The biggest so far was 12 or something,
wasn't it?

30:33.626 --> 30:36.062
And the guys are dumb too,
so they'll be easy to fleece.

30:37.864 --> 30:39.665
Do you want me to help out?

30:39.665 --> 30:41.534
Isn't this too good to pass up?

30:41.534 --> 30:43.402
At two hundred each,
plus whatever extras we tack on,

30:43.402 --> 30:44.670
do you know how much that is?

30:44.670 --> 30:45.805
It's a total jackpot, right?

30:46.506 --> 30:48.141
What date is it?

30:48.141 --> 30:49.442
It's 8 p.m. the day after tomorrow.

30:49.442 --> 30:50.943
Damn it, then that won't work.

30:50.943 --> 30:52.478
I've got something
I need to finish that day.

30:53.045 --> 30:55.047
- Call me next time. I'm hanging up.
- Wait, Mr. Ahn.

30:55.047 --> 30:56.949
Would next week work?

30:56.949 --> 30:58.050
There's an important gathering.

30:58.050 --> 30:59.952
There'll be about 50 people, so it's easy.

30:59.952 --> 31:00.853
Wait a second.

31:00.853 --> 31:02.088
What was the date again? Hold on.

31:02.088 --> 31:03.890
What are you talking about?
Hang up. I'm busy.

31:03.890 --> 31:05.591
Hey, you bastard, do as you're told.

31:05.591 --> 31:07.660
What kind of work
could a bastard like you possibly have?

31:07.660 --> 31:10.229
Fuck, please don't hang up.

31:10.229 --> 31:11.164
(Tracking location)

31:12.131 --> 31:13.232
What a psycho.

31:14.267 --> 31:15.168
Boss.

31:15.168 --> 31:16.202
We got him.

31:20.106 --> 31:21.073
Have a drink.

31:24.777 --> 31:27.847
(Mono)

31:43.396 --> 31:44.797
What you're saying is correct, sir.

31:45.398 --> 31:48.034
It's true that you achieved the results
within the promised period,

31:48.601 --> 31:49.769
and your request to separate
from headquarters...

31:50.937 --> 31:52.572
is justified, I believe.

31:53.840 --> 31:55.074
The vice chairman said...

31:55.741 --> 31:59.245
the person making the biggest issue out of
separating my company from headquarters...

32:00.046 --> 32:01.814
is you, the head of legal.

32:02.081 --> 32:04.016
Yes, that's right.

32:04.016 --> 32:05.117
And why is that?

32:05.451 --> 32:07.453
Because of Article 19...

32:07.453 --> 32:09.288
of the Mono Group bylaws, Clause Three.

32:10.056 --> 32:12.291
In the event of force majeure,

32:12.291 --> 32:13.659
company decision-making...

32:14.227 --> 32:17.096
must follow the decision
of the top executive.

32:17.997 --> 32:19.198
As you know,

32:19.198 --> 32:21.701
the vice chairman is temporarily
filling that role right now.

32:22.335 --> 32:24.270
So please understand
that we can't really do anything...

32:24.270 --> 32:26.272
about a matter the vice chairman opposes.

32:30.076 --> 32:32.912
Board Operations Regulation,
Article Five, Clause One.

32:32.912 --> 32:34.647
If the representative director is absent,

32:34.647 --> 32:37.517
a new person must be elected
through the board...

32:37.517 --> 32:39.752
within 60 days at most.

32:40.119 --> 32:42.054
But the date specified in the bylaws...

32:42.054 --> 32:43.322
has already passed.

32:44.790 --> 32:46.425
Calling that board meeting...

32:46.425 --> 32:48.361
isn't difficult in itself,

32:48.361 --> 32:51.063
but because careful consideration
takes time in choosing the right person,

32:51.063 --> 32:53.566
it would be hard to claim
that it's illegal.

32:54.000 --> 32:55.268
I'm sorry,

32:55.268 --> 32:56.602
but please wait just a little longer.

32:56.602 --> 32:59.705
It sounds like there's another reason
besides what you're saying.

33:21.327 --> 33:23.563
Would it be all right...

33:24.130 --> 33:25.364
if I spoke a little more frankly?

33:25.665 --> 33:26.933
Of course.

33:26.933 --> 33:27.767
Sir,

33:27.767 --> 33:30.436
there's no other way.
You should just file suit.

33:31.771 --> 33:33.706
The vice chairman won't listen to reason.

33:34.373 --> 33:36.309
Even when I tell him to start
by getting board approval,

33:36.309 --> 33:37.810
he shuts down completely.

33:39.312 --> 33:40.746
Even when I tell him
that if he keeps doing this,

33:40.746 --> 33:42.348
he'll have no choice
but to accept your demands,

33:42.348 --> 33:43.449
no matter how much
I try to persuade him...

33:43.449 --> 33:45.818
You must have had a hard time, sir.

33:48.788 --> 33:51.858
Problems between people
are all about emotion in the end,

33:51.858 --> 33:52.925
not logic.

33:53.259 --> 33:55.628
The vice chairman isn't going
to change going forward either.

33:57.430 --> 33:59.265
I've done everything I can,

34:00.133 --> 34:01.134
but it's not enough.

34:04.036 --> 34:06.105
All right, I've heard your proposal.

34:06.105 --> 34:07.507
Let's leave it here for today.

34:08.341 --> 34:09.809
Let's do that.

34:12.211 --> 34:13.179
Understood.

34:18.417 --> 34:19.485
Just keep looking ahead.

34:20.219 --> 34:21.687
He's probably trying to push you
into a lawsuit.

34:22.088 --> 34:24.323
He'd drag it out all the way
to a Supreme Court ruling,

34:24.323 --> 34:25.758
and expose every side of you...

34:25.758 --> 34:27.426
the public doesn't know. That's his goal.

34:28.094 --> 34:29.962
He'll keep provoking you.

34:29.962 --> 34:31.831
Is that the man Chief Kim mentioned?

34:31.831 --> 34:34.267
It seems he called in the head of legal
and gave him orders yesterday.

34:36.035 --> 34:38.204
If he hates me that much, what can I do?

34:38.204 --> 34:39.505
I have to give him what he wants.

34:40.606 --> 34:42.875
It was the first favor
that thoughtful friend ever asked.

34:42.875 --> 34:44.043
I fell short in many ways.

34:44.043 --> 34:45.578
No, it was enough.

34:45.578 --> 34:46.612
Thank you.

34:47.046 --> 34:48.881
You should check
your online accounts often too.

34:49.215 --> 34:51.083
There's a junior of his in IT...

34:51.384 --> 34:53.586
who's a total lunatic
and loves cracking hard passwords.

35:01.594 --> 35:03.062
What do you think you've got...

35:03.062 --> 35:05.665
to keep holding out for?

35:05.665 --> 35:07.834
You've got a lot of nerve.

35:07.834 --> 35:08.801
All right.

35:09.235 --> 35:11.537
All right, so please.

35:11.537 --> 35:13.206
If you were going to learn anyway,

35:13.206 --> 35:15.308
why learn it only now?

35:15.308 --> 35:16.742
If you'd learned before I came,

35:16.742 --> 35:19.278
how much better that would have been.

35:19.278 --> 35:20.546
I'm leaving...

35:20.546 --> 35:21.981
tomorrow first thing.

35:21.981 --> 35:22.882
Come out.

35:22.882 --> 35:24.150
- What are you doing?
- I said come out.

35:26.419 --> 35:29.188
No, you don't have to go anywhere.

35:29.188 --> 35:32.024
You all stay right where you are too.

35:32.358 --> 35:34.660
I'm stopping the demolition here today.

35:35.294 --> 35:37.663
Let's live seeing my face every day.

35:38.464 --> 35:40.500
Hey, how nice is that?

35:40.500 --> 35:43.469
There are plenty
of people here too, right?

35:45.271 --> 35:46.739
For a hundred years, a thousand years,

35:46.739 --> 35:49.242
keep doing business here...

35:50.076 --> 35:51.277
day in, day out.

35:54.914 --> 35:56.415
You little punks.

35:57.450 --> 35:59.385
What kind of stunt is this
in broad daylight?

36:01.320 --> 36:03.890
It seems we've got someone new...

36:03.890 --> 36:05.124
after a long time.

36:07.293 --> 36:08.127
What?

36:08.694 --> 36:09.629
Gi Cheol?

36:16.769 --> 36:20.039
I heard you made money,

36:20.840 --> 36:23.309
but I didn't know
you were holding out here too.

36:23.709 --> 36:25.645
Holding out? No.

36:25.845 --> 36:28.481
Come on,
the compensation must be pretty good.

36:28.915 --> 36:30.917
It must be nice for you.
You're making money.

36:31.918 --> 36:33.986
Stop harassing these people
and leave them alone.

36:34.754 --> 36:36.589
They're all moving out next week anyway.

36:36.589 --> 36:38.624
What? That soon?

36:38.624 --> 36:39.892
No.

36:39.892 --> 36:40.760
Sir.

36:40.760 --> 36:42.929
Tell them to hold out
just a few more days.

36:43.896 --> 36:46.432
They have no idea what I make in a day.
They can't end it already.

36:47.066 --> 36:49.869
These bastards are scared of everything.

36:51.270 --> 36:52.271
You psycho.

36:53.005 --> 36:55.107
I'm strapped for cash, sir.

36:55.708 --> 36:57.176
Let's stretch it out for just a few days.

36:57.577 --> 36:59.178
What about ten days?

36:59.612 --> 37:01.414
That's nonsense.

37:01.914 --> 37:02.849
Don't come back.

37:03.115 --> 37:04.317
Come on.

37:05.251 --> 37:07.520
We're all just trying to make a living.

37:07.520 --> 37:09.422
When things are rough,
we should help each other out.

37:10.256 --> 37:12.225
My wise prison buddy.

37:12.692 --> 37:14.160
Brother.

37:15.061 --> 37:16.195
Damn it.

37:17.997 --> 37:19.465
Sir.

37:20.933 --> 37:22.068
Hey.

37:24.770 --> 37:27.573
What is this, some spy movie?

37:27.573 --> 37:29.075
What are you doing?

37:30.376 --> 37:31.711
It just turned out this way.

37:31.711 --> 37:32.512
Have you been well?

37:32.512 --> 37:33.312
Yeah.

37:33.880 --> 37:35.715
You should've just come inside.

37:35.715 --> 37:36.816
Why didn't you?

37:37.383 --> 37:39.185
Did you commit a crime?

37:40.086 --> 37:41.988
There are too many ears at the station,

37:43.122 --> 37:44.724
and if I run into someone I know,

37:44.724 --> 37:46.359
it'll be, "Who came? Why'd he come?"

37:46.859 --> 37:48.261
I'm sick of that pointless chatter.

37:49.095 --> 37:51.197
All right, then spit it out.

37:51.397 --> 37:53.366
What is it
that's got you acting so serious?

37:53.599 --> 37:54.634
If it's not worth hearing,

37:54.634 --> 37:56.836
then you're buying lunch down there.

37:58.137 --> 37:59.405
Hangover soup and radish kimchi.

38:00.339 --> 38:01.641
Fine, I will.

38:03.176 --> 38:04.243
But Detective Kang,

38:05.111 --> 38:08.214
you handled the Jebudo Island
villa explosion case, didn't you?

38:09.015 --> 38:10.917
I'm the one working it now.

38:10.917 --> 38:12.185
My captain brought it over.

38:13.820 --> 38:14.654
Sir.

38:15.788 --> 38:17.723
If I'd thought
you were going to ask me that,

38:17.723 --> 38:19.058
I wouldn't have come out.

38:20.159 --> 38:22.695
Come on, just tell me.

38:23.095 --> 38:24.797
Hey, maybe other guys would,

38:24.797 --> 38:26.999
but you're not the type
to investigate a case this half-assed.

38:29.302 --> 38:30.536
So why did you this time?

38:31.671 --> 38:34.006
I heard Captain Son resigned
because of a chronic condition.

38:34.774 --> 38:36.042
Then...

38:36.042 --> 38:38.678
you should've at least wrapped up the case
before transferring.

38:38.678 --> 38:40.480
What was so urgent that you moved here?

38:42.515 --> 38:44.650
You're hiding something, aren't you?

38:45.084 --> 38:47.119
It was all complete bullshit.

38:48.821 --> 38:49.589
What?

38:51.257 --> 38:53.025
You know my captain well, don't you?

38:53.659 --> 38:55.628
When he takes a case,
he's sharp as a knife.

38:55.962 --> 38:57.497
That's what I admired about him,

38:57.497 --> 39:00.233
so I was turning down offers
from senior guys.

39:00.800 --> 39:02.201
But that wasn't it.

39:02.835 --> 39:05.538
It turns out
I completely misjudged the man...

39:05.538 --> 39:08.040
or maybe he changed for some reason.

39:16.149 --> 39:18.017
I mean,
he was like Cinderella or something.

39:18.651 --> 39:21.020
Every chance he got, he'd disappear.

39:21.454 --> 39:24.457
And whatever he got, he got a big one.

39:24.991 --> 39:26.726
I got a bad feeling right away.

39:37.103 --> 39:37.870
Sir.

39:40.506 --> 39:41.808
The captain quit.

39:42.475 --> 39:43.342
What?

39:43.576 --> 39:44.510
You didn't know?

39:47.547 --> 39:48.447
And guess what?

39:49.215 --> 39:51.551
The man who told me even
how many times he went to the bathroom...

39:51.551 --> 39:53.653
did all that without a single word.

39:53.653 --> 39:56.656
Nobody ever heard
he was sick enough to take medical leave.

39:56.923 --> 39:58.224
What kind of bullshit is that?

39:58.791 --> 40:00.126
So I got fed up,

40:00.526 --> 40:02.528
and walked away from it myself.

40:03.262 --> 40:05.798
Did you tell anyone about...

40:05.798 --> 40:06.666
No.

40:06.866 --> 40:07.867
Did you report it to your superiors?

40:08.634 --> 40:09.769
That's enough.

40:10.269 --> 40:12.538
You know full well I could never do that.

40:15.575 --> 40:16.409
Right now,

40:17.510 --> 40:20.413
there isn't a single piece of evidence
left in this case.

40:20.980 --> 40:22.014
And this...

40:23.115 --> 40:24.150
wasn't arson.

40:24.350 --> 40:26.118
- It wasn't?
- At the scene,

40:26.586 --> 40:29.288
they found a weapon
believed to have been used in the crime,

40:29.288 --> 40:30.690
and it's undergoing detailed forensics.

40:32.592 --> 40:34.026
So it's a murder case.

40:38.197 --> 40:40.500
That's the only evidence
I barely managed to find.

40:41.134 --> 40:42.168
There's nothing else.

40:43.603 --> 40:45.905
When you first started investigating,

40:45.905 --> 40:47.240
did you find anything?

40:47.240 --> 40:49.308
Or do you remember anything at all?

40:49.308 --> 40:51.811
I walked away from all of it.
What would I know?

40:51.811 --> 40:54.347
It'd be quicker to ask Captain Son.

40:54.347 --> 40:57.283
Even if he knows, he'll say he doesn't.

40:57.283 --> 40:58.885
Don't do this.

40:59.152 --> 40:59.952
Hey!

40:59.952 --> 41:02.355
Do you think I'd have come
all the way here if I weren't desperate?

41:03.589 --> 41:05.091
I was surprised too.

41:05.558 --> 41:07.393
If some junior of yours
had gone off and died...

41:07.393 --> 41:10.363
and gotten buried somewhere,
you probably wouldn't even know.

41:12.465 --> 41:13.266
Hey!

41:13.666 --> 41:14.834
Are you really doing this?

41:15.501 --> 41:18.204
When you finally moved into a lease place
from a monthly rental last year,

41:18.204 --> 41:19.906
who lent you the money?

41:19.906 --> 41:21.307
And without interest too.

41:21.307 --> 41:22.942
Seriously?

41:22.942 --> 41:23.876
I'll pay you back.

41:23.876 --> 41:26.579
Then what were you doing
that you're only showing up now?

41:26.579 --> 41:29.215
Even if we're on different teams,
if you cared at all,

41:29.215 --> 41:31.117
how did you not know
I was suffering like that?

41:31.651 --> 41:32.985
What, were you dating or something?

41:33.786 --> 41:34.720
What?

41:36.155 --> 41:38.057
You know well I'm not some half-assed cop,

41:38.558 --> 41:40.426
and now you're showing up asking me?

41:41.794 --> 41:42.595
Detective Kang.

41:43.229 --> 41:44.096
Did you maybe...

41:45.097 --> 41:47.567
The villa CCTV hard drive...

41:48.701 --> 41:50.269
didn't burn up and disappear.

41:51.070 --> 41:52.438
It was taken out beforehand.

41:53.973 --> 41:54.907
Taken out?

41:54.907 --> 41:55.741
By who?

41:56.142 --> 41:58.311
Good grief.

41:59.111 --> 42:00.580
Have you really lost your touch?

42:02.448 --> 42:05.151
Out of those four people, two are dead,

42:06.018 --> 42:07.487
so aren't there only two left?

42:08.354 --> 42:10.456
Do you really have to experience more
to know what's behind it?

42:12.725 --> 42:14.093
It's obvious.

42:18.064 --> 42:20.233
(Wang Gi Cheol)

42:54.967 --> 42:56.002
Hello?

43:00.940 --> 43:03.009
My name is Ham Myo Jin.

43:06.179 --> 43:07.013
Hello?

43:14.053 --> 43:15.154
How have you been?

43:16.355 --> 43:17.156
Pardon?

43:17.924 --> 43:19.325
When I heard about your accident,

43:21.160 --> 43:22.195
I was worried.

43:22.728 --> 43:23.596
Do you...

43:24.263 --> 43:25.598
know me well?

43:27.266 --> 43:28.868
Because of the shock from the accident,

43:28.868 --> 43:30.169
I lost my memory.

43:31.037 --> 43:33.706
I'm recovering now,
but I still can't remember much.

43:34.740 --> 43:37.043
Then how did you know to call?

43:37.410 --> 43:39.378
I found the phone I'd lost,

43:39.712 --> 43:41.247
and saw the text messages and called.

43:42.181 --> 43:43.516
We used to keep in touch a lot,

43:43.516 --> 43:45.084
so I thought you might be able to help me.

43:45.685 --> 43:46.586
Interesting.

43:47.453 --> 43:49.822
So you've gone all the way
back to the beginning?

43:50.690 --> 43:51.524
Pardon?

43:52.024 --> 43:53.326
You mean you don't even remember...

43:54.694 --> 43:56.762
who I am now, right?

44:00.399 --> 44:01.501
Please tell me.

44:02.135 --> 44:03.603
How do I know you?

44:05.171 --> 44:06.472
You don't need to be curious.

44:07.640 --> 44:09.575
If you know, it puts us both in danger.

44:09.575 --> 44:12.278
Hang up this call and delete my number.

44:12.712 --> 44:14.514
Not that I'd answer again anyway.

44:14.514 --> 44:15.882
I met Lee Jong Su.

44:16.782 --> 44:18.251
He had an accident.

44:19.051 --> 44:20.319
He's in the hospital right now.

44:23.456 --> 44:24.524
Hello?

44:25.324 --> 44:26.192
Who did it?

44:27.360 --> 44:28.194
What?

44:28.394 --> 44:30.196
Who did that to him?

44:31.631 --> 44:32.532
Don't tell me...

44:33.533 --> 44:34.567
it was you.

44:36.536 --> 44:37.937
I'll tell you in person.

44:38.938 --> 44:39.839
Everything.

44:42.375 --> 44:47.446
(Redevelopment has us furious.
We oppose it again and again.)

45:13.172 --> 45:17.944
(Star Karaoke Bar)

45:58.651 --> 45:59.952
Why did you come back?

46:08.261 --> 46:10.096
Go ahead, bastard.

46:11.931 --> 46:13.132
I warned you.

46:13.132 --> 46:15.067
Nothing good comes from us meeting.

46:15.535 --> 46:16.536
I just...

46:17.737 --> 46:19.438
want my memory back.

46:19.972 --> 46:21.207
That's why I came here.

46:21.641 --> 46:23.342
What happened to Jong Su?

46:23.342 --> 46:25.478
I found out
he had been blackmailing my friend,

46:25.478 --> 46:26.779
so I went to see him.

46:27.113 --> 46:28.781
To ask what had happened.

46:38.758 --> 46:40.326
But Choi Hee Su is dead.

46:41.661 --> 46:42.929
You know Hee Su?

46:43.429 --> 46:44.430
How do you know her?

46:45.097 --> 46:46.532
What are you to her?

46:46.532 --> 46:47.800
When I stopped hearing from you,

46:50.203 --> 46:52.939
I thought you'd forgotten everything
and started over.

46:52.939 --> 46:53.940
Please.

46:54.807 --> 46:56.476
Tell me what you know about me.

47:16.362 --> 47:17.230
You.

47:18.931 --> 47:19.765
How much...

47:20.366 --> 47:22.135
do you know right now?

47:24.537 --> 47:25.438
At first,

47:26.806 --> 47:28.374
I thought I was trash
who betrayed my friend...

47:29.675 --> 47:32.145
and stole her boyfriend,

47:34.714 --> 47:36.649
but that happened...

47:37.416 --> 47:40.486
while I was trying to meet
Chairman Choi Young Ho for some reason.

47:42.655 --> 47:44.323
You know what that reason is, don't you?

47:45.057 --> 47:46.359
I'm warning you.

47:46.959 --> 47:48.361
Forget everything and live on.

47:49.629 --> 47:51.464
That's what's best for you.

47:52.698 --> 47:54.967
No, I need to know.

47:55.802 --> 47:58.504
Why I ended up stealing
my friend's boyfriend,

47:58.504 --> 48:00.907
and why I was trying to meet Chairman
Choi Young Ho, a man I didn't even know.

48:01.440 --> 48:03.776
Your old self is starting to come back.

48:06.345 --> 48:08.981
That vicious look
from when you came at me with this knife,

48:09.782 --> 48:11.484
saying you'd kill me.

48:12.118 --> 48:13.052
I...

48:14.554 --> 48:15.922
did that to you?

48:46.886 --> 48:48.754
That was when you were
in your third year of middle school.

48:49.555 --> 48:53.292
Your parents were always smiling,

48:55.027 --> 48:56.496
and they were deeply religious.

49:02.635 --> 49:04.337
The church...

49:05.538 --> 49:06.539
my mom and dad attended.

49:11.043 --> 49:12.411
From then on,

49:12.411 --> 49:14.547
everything started going wrong.

49:25.391 --> 49:26.559
There was an accident.

49:29.095 --> 49:30.196
Your family of three...

49:31.197 --> 49:33.132
lived in a greenhouse...

49:34.433 --> 49:35.935
because your father grew flowers.

49:38.070 --> 49:39.906
(Cheongham Farm)

49:41.941 --> 49:44.577
The day a fire broke out
and everything burned down,

49:45.244 --> 49:46.612
your parents died,

49:49.248 --> 49:50.883
and only you barely survived.

49:51.517 --> 49:53.186
What?

49:54.687 --> 49:55.922
The people in the neighborhood...

49:56.856 --> 49:58.391
hated me...

50:00.059 --> 50:01.394
saying I was just an unemployed bum,

50:02.528 --> 50:04.964
but your parents were the only ones
who were different.

50:05.798 --> 50:07.600
They treated me like a human being.

50:08.267 --> 50:09.469
- What are you saying?
- You...

50:10.536 --> 50:12.038
were polite,

50:13.639 --> 50:15.675
and a good student too.

50:17.109 --> 50:18.277
That was when it hit me.

50:20.346 --> 50:22.048
By the time I came to my senses,

50:23.149 --> 50:24.650
everything was already over.

50:24.650 --> 50:25.451
What...

50:26.185 --> 50:27.420
are you talking about right now?

50:27.420 --> 50:28.454
Just listen.

50:30.022 --> 50:31.157
There's a reason.

50:31.924 --> 50:34.360
(15 years ago)

50:34.360 --> 50:36.863
You killed those good people for money?

50:37.230 --> 50:39.065
You bastard.

50:39.065 --> 50:40.800
They were people who lived honestly.

50:41.400 --> 50:42.502
Why would you kill them?

50:42.502 --> 50:44.237
And you still call yourself human?

50:44.237 --> 50:46.806
You die too, you beast.

50:46.806 --> 50:48.841
Die!

50:48.841 --> 50:50.309
Goodness.

50:54.013 --> 50:55.648
You bastard.

50:56.482 --> 50:57.650
You evil bastard.

50:58.751 --> 50:59.952
That damned bastard.

51:04.390 --> 51:05.491
Myo Jin!

51:06.926 --> 51:07.793
Die.

51:08.060 --> 51:09.829
- Myo Jin, don't.
- Die!

51:12.165 --> 51:13.399
You die too!

51:13.800 --> 51:16.269
Let go of me! I'm going to kill him!

51:16.269 --> 51:17.670
I'm going to kill him!

51:17.670 --> 51:18.604
Hey!

51:24.844 --> 51:27.213
Where are you taking her right now?

51:27.213 --> 51:28.948
The suspect is injured,
so they both need to come with us first.

51:28.948 --> 51:29.782
Move aside.

51:29.782 --> 51:31.984
Her mother and father died overnight.

51:31.984 --> 51:33.886
How could she be in her right mind?

51:33.886 --> 51:35.488
Don't you feel sorry for the poor child?

51:35.888 --> 51:37.490
So what if you're a cop?

51:37.490 --> 51:38.891
I can't stand watching this.

51:40.326 --> 51:41.394
Let go.

51:41.394 --> 51:42.428
Go!

51:42.428 --> 51:44.397
Myo Jin, it's okay.

51:49.802 --> 51:50.970
It's okay.

51:51.804 --> 51:53.539
- Where are you going?
- Myo Jin, what is it all of a sudden?

52:03.149 --> 52:04.083
It's okay.

52:05.751 --> 52:06.586
Myo Jin.

52:32.645 --> 52:33.513
This...

52:34.747 --> 52:37.216
is the gift you gave me that day.

52:37.216 --> 52:38.284
You...

52:40.253 --> 52:42.221
killed my mom and dad?

52:42.455 --> 52:44.790
That's how I ended up going to prison,

52:47.460 --> 52:49.362
and I heard...

52:49.362 --> 52:51.264
the church your parents attended
took you in.

52:52.098 --> 52:54.066
I wanted to tell you the truth,

52:54.934 --> 52:57.770
but I thought
one tragedy ought to be enough.

52:59.005 --> 53:00.506
I prayed in prison...

53:01.607 --> 53:03.109
that you would forget all of this,

53:04.143 --> 53:05.411
and live a new life,

53:07.246 --> 53:09.048
that you'd be freed...

53:10.383 --> 53:11.551
from this hellish reality.

53:12.018 --> 53:13.219
What are you saying?

53:13.219 --> 53:14.821
But it was useless.

53:17.190 --> 53:19.826
It's been a little over two years now...

53:20.393 --> 53:22.195
because it was right after
I got out of prison.

53:27.233 --> 53:29.168
You came holding that knife,

53:31.003 --> 53:32.104
saying you'd kill me...

53:33.606 --> 53:35.608
and avenge your parents.

53:37.343 --> 53:38.244
Stop.

53:38.978 --> 53:40.346
You were such a good kid,

53:41.881 --> 53:44.083
but you'd turned into a complete monster.

53:46.486 --> 53:47.787
You must've been furious too...

53:49.121 --> 53:50.890
because you became an orphan overnight.

53:50.890 --> 53:52.458
- Please stop!
- I can tell...

53:53.426 --> 53:55.027
just by looking into someone's eyes...

53:57.029 --> 54:00.666
whether they really can
kill someone or not.

54:01.601 --> 54:02.568
And you...

54:03.503 --> 54:05.771
really looked like you could kill someone.

54:06.873 --> 54:09.041
Your desire to get revenge on me
turned you into a devil.

54:09.041 --> 54:09.876
Shut up.

54:10.476 --> 54:11.911
Please, shut up!

54:11.911 --> 54:13.713
Be quiet and listen to the end.

54:14.514 --> 54:16.482
I haven't even started yet.

54:21.287 --> 54:23.122
I don't need anything else.
Just tell me...

54:23.556 --> 54:25.558
whether you killed my mom and dad.

54:28.127 --> 54:29.061
Myo Jin!

54:30.863 --> 54:32.198
Do you miss your parents?

54:32.732 --> 54:34.734
Do you need to see blood
before you'll be satisfied?

54:35.201 --> 54:36.636
If you want revenge,

54:37.036 --> 54:38.905
get your head on straight first.

54:43.843 --> 54:45.545
Don't talk nonsense!

54:45.545 --> 54:48.181
Hey, you tailed Ham Myo Jin
behind my back, didn't you?

54:48.181 --> 54:50.616
You thought there'd be money in it,
so you wanted it all for yourself?

54:50.950 --> 54:52.151
Have you lost your mind?

54:52.151 --> 54:53.386
No.

54:53.386 --> 54:56.556
It just kind of ended up that way.

54:58.090 --> 55:00.693
Hey, if you keep this up,
there'll be nothing left for you.

55:00.927 --> 55:02.995
Hey, what about Ryu Jun Ho?

55:03.463 --> 55:05.798
He doesn't know a damn thing,

55:05.798 --> 55:06.833
so you just worry about your side.

55:06.833 --> 55:08.501
Okay, I'll call after I finish.

55:10.536 --> 55:12.271
That's it. Let's go.

55:13.239 --> 55:14.140
Young Gu.

55:14.540 --> 55:15.541
Get them ready.

55:15.541 --> 55:16.609
Yes, boss.

55:17.443 --> 55:18.277
Ready!

55:18.277 --> 55:19.212
Ready.

55:29.589 --> 55:30.456
What's that?

55:33.960 --> 55:34.827
What?

55:35.194 --> 55:36.362
What do you mean, all of a sudden?

55:36.662 --> 55:37.730
Can you see who it is?

55:38.097 --> 55:40.266
The windows are blacked out.
I can't see anything inside.

55:41.033 --> 55:42.835
There's someone else besides us...

55:42.835 --> 55:44.303
who's after Ham Myo Jin?

55:44.303 --> 55:45.538
Hey, forget it.

55:45.538 --> 55:46.772
We're ignoring it and going in.

55:47.240 --> 55:48.307
We won't get a chance like this again.

55:48.307 --> 55:50.643
Don't be insane.
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

55:50.643 --> 55:52.478
Stop talking shit and pull out now.

55:52.478 --> 55:53.746
There are still businesses open here.

55:53.746 --> 55:54.981
It must be somebody from one of them.

55:54.981 --> 55:56.682
What are you scared of?

55:56.682 --> 55:59.051
Don't make me repeat myself.

55:59.051 --> 56:00.386
Pull out now.

56:00.386 --> 56:03.055
If you don't,
you and I are done as of today.

56:04.423 --> 56:05.825
Hey, you...

56:05.825 --> 56:06.659
Hello?

56:06.893 --> 56:09.595
This rude bitch
has really pushed it too far.

56:09.595 --> 56:10.530
Hey, everybody out.

56:15.501 --> 56:16.869
This is easy.

56:16.869 --> 56:18.104
That woman from the photo
I showed you earlier.

56:18.104 --> 56:20.106
The second you grab her, get her out fast.

56:20.339 --> 56:21.707
Yes, boss.

56:21.707 --> 56:22.542
Let's go.

56:25.912 --> 56:28.114
(We're struggling enough just to get by,
so why talk about redevelopment?)

56:28.114 --> 56:30.650
(Absolutely against
reckless redevelopment)

56:33.452 --> 56:34.587
Hey, is this the place?

56:34.987 --> 56:36.622
There isn't even a rat in sight.

56:37.156 --> 56:39.025
This is the latest model,
so I'm sure of it.

56:40.560 --> 56:41.794
Hey, stop the car.

56:42.228 --> 56:43.329
I think there are people here.

56:58.544 --> 57:00.680
Yeah, that's the car Mr. An's goons use.

57:02.248 --> 57:03.149
What do you mean?

57:03.683 --> 57:05.685
Whenever I drugged the drinks
and made the customers lose it,

57:06.118 --> 57:07.920
Mr. An's goons would come.

57:07.920 --> 57:10.223
And they always
hauled them off in that car.

57:10.223 --> 57:12.458
It's nice seeing those bastards here.

57:13.926 --> 57:14.727
What?

57:15.127 --> 57:16.562
Look at you, idiot.

57:35.548 --> 57:37.083
How'd you get your hands on that?

57:37.083 --> 57:39.352
I got it from a vet.

57:45.391 --> 57:46.592
Do we just leave him there?

57:48.060 --> 57:49.128
He'll be fine.

57:50.563 --> 57:51.597
Let's make this quick.

57:57.770 --> 57:58.805
But...

57:58.805 --> 58:01.107
do you know
what this Mr. An guy looks like?

58:01.107 --> 58:02.675
How would I?

58:02.675 --> 58:03.810
Have you seen him, boss?

58:09.816 --> 58:12.185
You put that punk to sleep
without even knowing what he looks like?

58:17.824 --> 58:18.925
Wake him back up.

58:19.358 --> 58:21.661
Maybe I should kill you today,
you blockheaded bastard.

58:21.661 --> 58:22.562
I'm sorry.

58:22.562 --> 58:24.096
I'll wake him up right away.

58:29.001 --> 58:30.436
Wake up, you fat bastard.

58:32.271 --> 58:33.306
I'm sleepy.

58:33.306 --> 58:34.607
My ass you are.

58:34.607 --> 58:35.942
If you don't get up, I'll kill you.

58:40.546 --> 58:41.447
What?

58:53.693 --> 58:54.994
What's that now?

59:32.031 --> 59:36.469
(REVERSE)

59:36.669 --> 59:38.571
If she went out anyway,
you should've followed her,

59:38.571 --> 59:40.206
or at least known where she was going.

59:40.206 --> 59:41.774
They're not easy people,

59:41.774 --> 59:43.776
so things could get ugly.

59:43.776 --> 59:45.111
Don't stop.

59:45.111 --> 59:47.480
What if they end up dead?

59:47.480 --> 59:49.115
This isn't what I used to take.

59:49.115 --> 59:51.017
Jun Ho said the hospital changed
your medication.

59:51.017 --> 59:52.985
Do I really need that?

59:53.252 --> 59:54.287
The two of them are working together,

59:54.287 --> 59:55.822
trying to get rid of that woman.

59:55.822 --> 59:56.956
Where's your boss?

59:56.956 --> 01:00:00.126
What kind of trouble are you asking for
sticking with that woman?

01:00:00.726 --> 01:00:03.496
Ham Myo Jin has another agenda too?

01:00:03.996 --> 01:00:05.998
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
